Banco Popolare May Soon Sell Hungarian Subsidiary, Sole Reports

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 
2011-08-21T09:52:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/banco-popolare-may-soon-sell-hungarian-subsidiary-sole-reports.html
Banco Popolare SC (BP) ,  Italy ’s fourth-
biggest bank, is in advanced talks to sell its Hungarian
subsidiary to a local financier, Il Sole 24 Ore reported,
without saying how it got the information.  The sale isn’t on the agenda of the board meeting scheduled
for Aug. 26 to approve first-half results, the newspaper said,
adding that Popolare plans to exit  Croatia  after  Hungary .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francesca Cinelli in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Ludden at 
 jludden@bloomberg.net  